Question: Which of the following indicates potential overfitting of a machine learning model?
Answer: The model performs poorly on training data and on validation data.
The model performs poorly on training data and well on validation data.
The model performs well on training data and on validation data.
The model performs well on training data but poorly on validation data.
Correct: The model performs well on training data but poorly on validation data.
